OL,3,CDriver charged with attempted murder
OL,4,Cafter five people hit by car
OL,6,FA driver has been charged with five
OL,7,Fcounts of attempted murder after five
OL,8,Fpedestrians were injured by a car on a
OL,9,Fbusy London road.
OL,11,FThree of the five people were taken to
OL,12,Fhospital after the incident on Ealing
OL,13,FBroadway, west London, at about 2.30pm
OL,14,Fon Saturday.
OL,16,FTimir Ahmed Mohamed, 34, of Grange
OL,17,FPark, Ealing, was also charged with
OL,18,Fdangerous driving, failing to stop,
OL,19,Ffailing to provide a specimen of
OL,20,Fbreath for analysis, and criminal
OL,21,Fdamage, the Met Police said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
