OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FMohamed was remanded into custody and
OL,12,Fwill appear at Willesden Magistrates'
OL,13,FCourt on Monday.
OL,15,FCounter Terrorism Policing London
OL,16,Fconducted initial inquiries, but the
OL,17,Fincident is not being treated as
OL,18,Fterrorism.
