OL,3,CDriver charged with attempted murder
OL,4,Cafter five people hit by car
OL,6,FNone of the injuries were life-
OL,7,Fthreatening, and the two people who
OL,8,Fwere not taken to hospital received
OL,9,Ftreatment at the scene.
OL,11,F"We sent a number of resources
OL,12,Fincluding ambulance crews, paramedics
OL,13,Fin fast response cars, a volunteer
OL,14,Femergency responder crew and an
OL,15,Fincident response officer to the
OL,16,Fscene," a London Ambulance Service
OL,17,Fspokesperson said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/4
