OL,3,CDriver charged with attempted murder
OL,4,Cafter five people hit by car
OL,6,F"We also dispatched London's Air
OL,7,FAmbulance. We treated three patients
OL,8,Fat the scene and took one of them to a
OL,9,Fmajor trauma centre by road as a
OL,10,Fpriority. The other two patients were
OL,11,Ftaken to a local hospital."
